commit 468bb54980f597fffed2f268f9b52c616fcb325e
Author: Jérôme Piquot <jpiquot@itaneo.com>
Date:   Mon May 18 09:48:52 2026 +0200

    Add preflight check results and Personal Data Inventory tests
    
    - Created multiple JSON files for preflight check results, all indicating failures due to dirty paths in the working tree.
    - Implemented `PersonalDataInventoryTests` to ensure proper classification of personal data properties and containers.
    - Added checks for organization entity fields to remain unmarked by default.
    - Verified that all inspected contract properties are classified correctly.

